description: Describes a previously submitted calculation execution.

nested_items.name: SessionId
nested_items.description: The session ID that the calculation ran in.

nested_items.name: Description
nested_items.description: The description of the calculation execution.

nested_items.name: WorkingDirectory
nested_items.description: The Amazon S3 location in which calculation results are stored.

nested_items.name: SubmissionDateTime
nested_items.description: The date and time the calculation was submitted for processing.

nested_items.name: CompletionDateTime
nested_items.description: The date and time the calculation completed processing.

nested_items.name: State
nested_items.description: The state of the calculation execution. A description of each state follows.

nested_items.name: StateChangeReason
nested_items.description: The reason for the calculation state change (for example, the calculation was canceled because the session was terminated).

nested_items.name: Statistics
nested_items.description: Contains information about the data processing unit (DPU) execution time and progress. This field is populated only when statistics are available.

nested_items.name: DpuExecutionInMillis
nested_items.description: The data processing unit execution time in milliseconds for the calculation.

nested_items.name: StdOutS3Uri
nested_items.description: The Amazon S3 location of the stdout file for the calculation.

nested_items.name: StdErrorS3Uri
nested_items.description: The Amazon S3 location of the stderr error messages file for the calculation.

nested_items.name: ResultS3Uri
nested_items.description: The Amazon S3 location of the folder for the calculation results.

nested_items.name: ResultType
nested_items.description: The data format of the calculation result.
